sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI LMEval Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMES as LMES Job Pod<br/>quay.io/rhoai/odh-ta-lmes-job-rhel9
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelSvc as Model Serving Endpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTP(S)
    participant Output as Output Path<br/>(PVC/stdout)

    Note over Operator,Output: Flow 1: Local Model Evaluation
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job/Pod<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>LMES: Schedule Pod
    LMES->>HFHub: Download model weights & tokenizer<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
    HFHub-->>LMES: Model artifacts
    Note over LMES: Run evaluation locally<br/>(GPU/CPU in-process)
    LMES->>Output: Write results<br/>Filesystem

    Note over Operator,Output: Flow 2: API-based Model Evaluation (Remote)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job/Pod<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>LMES: Schedule Pod
    loop For each evaluation sample
        LMES->>ModelSvc: POST inference request<br/>HTTP(S)/8080<br/>Bearer Token / None
        ModelSvc-->>LMES: Inference response
    end
    LMES->>Output: Write results<br/>Filesystem

    Note over Operator,Output: Flow 3: S3 Model Artifact Download
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job/Pod<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>LMES: Schedule Pod
    LMES->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>LMES: Model files → hf_home cache
    Note over LMES: Run evaluation locally
    LMES->>Output: Write results<br/>Filesystem
